HEADWORD: Praxis
<hw>Prax"is</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/, fr.
<?/ to do. See <er>Practice</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Use; practice;
especially, exercise or discipline for a specific purpose or
